If you know of a better or easier way, please let us know.
This has been a relatively easy approach.

--------------
Installation
--------------

git clone git://github.com/mmullis/coverize.git coverize
cd coverize
make
cd ..
sudo mv coverize <YOUR ERLANG INSTALLATION LIB DIRECTORY>



--------------
Updating
--------------
cd <YOUR ERLANG INSTALLATION LIB DIRECTORY>/coverize
git pull origin master
